  "text": "Each subject underwent echocardiographic examination in the Department of Cardiology, Ninewells Hospital, by operators who were unaware of the other measurements using a Hewlett Packard Sonos 2500 (Hewlett Packard, Andover, MA, USA). The left ventricular wall thickness and size were calculated from M-mode measurements. Left ventricular mass index (LVMI) was calculated indexed to body surface area. [CITATION_1] ",
